{"tid":2324272,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"韋利安：阿森納告訴我 想三年內贏歐聯","createTime":"2020-12-13T22:14:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-14T05:59:59.000Z","uid":5655,"like":35,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"d7a3856bea80cd8e49702337569baf01fbaf0c36","tid":2324272,"uid":5655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T22:14:56.000Z","msg":"阿森納今夏第一筆簽約是韋利安（Willian），日前他接受了《太陽報》的採訪，他親承想和阿森納一起贏得歐聯冠軍。<br />\n　　韋利安表示，阿森納告訴他計劃三年內贏得歐聯冠軍。韋利安透露：「當我和主教練談話時，他告訴我為什麼和我簽了三年合約。」<br />\n　　「主教練首先的考慮是想要贏得歐聯參賽資格，然後在我離開時贏得歐聯冠軍，這也是我想要聽到的。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.soccer.sina.com.hk/news/article/12072817/7116/20200821\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.soccer.sina.com.hk%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F12072817%2F7116%2F20200821&d=WHMLQMiyWmfm849WKe725C3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=ea2ff7a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.soccer.sina.com.hk/news/article/12072817/7116/20200821</a>"},{"pid":"7840bc08fb7d355240d5b04b666fc3e2d2013873","tid":2324272,"uid":227271,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T22:19:28.000Z","msg":"咪啱囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟返支那叫法<br />\n<br />\n歐足總歐洲聯賽<br />\n<br />\n咁咪歐聯囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"638e2c365e85b34b7f6803fc398b62b213c1635c","tid":2324272,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T23:15:07.000Z","msg":"首先今季要護級成功"},{"pid":"faeec23e58b55095d78f34e3200ca045175a8f08","tid":2324272,"uid":186431,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T23:20:14.000Z","msg":"想三年內贏英冠<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98234dc0afe3dce602f6f014041145a73140e567","tid":2324272,"uid":83667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T23:27:23.000Z","msg":"三年又三年三年又三年"},{"pid":"fe4255fd0c9b582be278c443bac2d1f85bef93fb","tid":2324272,"uid":165817,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7840bc08fb